IntroContentTitle: SpeakFast is a great English-learning project!
IntroContentText: It's a community of both English native and non-native speaking teachers that developed their unique study approaches!
MiddleBlockContentTitle: A unique study method will let student achieve great results!
MiddleBlockContentText: Our approach greatly increases student's involvement into process. After classes they will like English learning. There is almost no boring theoretical exercises but instead fascinating game playing that models real world situations. We will create English speaking environment for every student.
ProductLunchText: We believe we are a multi-culture school with the best teachers from all over the world. Here you can find a teacher that will help you to reach any goal you set. For example, the teacher will help you get into the university of your dream or develop the ability to read English literature without translating services.
AboutUsText: SpeakFast - is not just a school but community. Every day we publish news, games, tests in our social networks. We want our students to walk outside the box and get deep insight into English-speaking atmosphere.
AboutContentText: Achievement is very important part of study process. The achievements of our students is exactly what motivates us to become better!
ContactContentText: Our manager will contact you within 2 business days.
